Administrative Staff Required In Lahore Leads University
Posted by:
in
3 days ago
LAHORE LEADS UNIVERSITY
Administrative Staff Required
LAHORE LEADS UNIVERSITY is one ofthose growing educational institutions which possess a prominent and distinct room among other educational institutions in providing a quality education. The strategic expansion in different departments require capable individuals, so. LAHORE LEADS UNIVERSITY invites applications for Administrative Positions in the following departments.
1- Registrar Office
Additional Registrar
Master’s Degree with minimum 7-10 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized Institution
Deputy Registrar
Master’s Degree with minimum 5 years experience
Assistant Registrar
Master’s Degree with minimum 2 years experience
2- Office of Examinations
Additional Controller of Examination
Master’s Degree with minimum 7-10 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized institution
Deputy Controller of Examination
Master’s Degree with minimum 5 years experience
3- Treasurer Office
Additional Treasurer
Master’s Degree with minimum 7-10 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized institution
Deputy Treasurer
Master’s Degree with minimum 5 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized Institution
4- Assistant Director QEC
Experience
BS/Master’s Degree with minimum 2 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized Institution
5- Chief Library Officer
Master’s in library sciences in the 7-10 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized institution
6- Assistant Director R&D
Experience
BS/Master’s Degree with minimum 2 years of relevant experience in an HEC recognized Institution
7- I.T. Department
Network Administrator
BS/Master Degree with minimum 5 years of relevant experience
Assistant Network Administrator
BS/Master Degree with minimum 5 of relevant experience
8- Chief Security Officer
Retired Army Officer will be preferred with minimum 10 years of experience
9- Marketing Department
Marketing Executives
MBA/BBA Degree with minimum 1 year of relevant experience
Admission Officers
Master’s Degree with minimum 1 year of relevant experience
Experience
10- Executive Secretary (Male)
Experience
Master’s Degree with minimum 3 years of relevant experience with excellent communication skills
11- Front Office
Receptionist /Telephone Operator
Bachelor’s Degree with minimum 2 years of relevant experience with excellent communication skills
Remuneration: Competitive salary packages will be offered to suitable applicants.
Applications: Applicants should state full particulars in their CVs, including academic qualifications (with %/CGPA), institutions attended. The position applied for should be clearly stated on the envelope/email.
Post your applications to President LAHORE LEADS UNIV ERSITY or E-mail at ceo@leads.edu.pk
LAHORE LEADS UNIVERSITY 5-Tipu Block, New Garden Town Lahore. E-mail: cco@leads.edu.pk
2014-05-03
